<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Explore Italy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        header {
            background: #ff6347; /* Tomato color */
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .intro {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .intro img {
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 600px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .attractions, .activities, .food {
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #ff6347; /* Tomato color */
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: square;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            background: #ff6347; /* Tomato color */
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Italy</h1>
        <p>Your dream destination awaits!</p>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <section class="intro">
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/04/Colosseum_in_Rome%2C_Italy_%28cropped%29.jpg" alt="Colosseum in Rome">
            <h2>Why Visit Italy?</h2>
            <p>Italy is known for its rich history, stunning architecture, and mouthwatering cuisine. From the canals of Venice to the rolling hills of Tuscany, every corner offers something unique!</p>
        </section>
        
        <section class="attractions">
            <h2>Top Attractions</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>The Colosseum</li>
                <li>Venice Canals</li>
                <li>Pisa's Leaning Tower</li>
                <li>Vatican City</li>
                <li>Florence's Duomo</li>
            </ul>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e0/Venice_%28Canal%29.jpg" alt="Venice Canals">
        </section>

        <section class="activities">
            <h2>Things to Do</h2>
            <p>Experience authentic Italian cuisine, explore ancient ruins, take a gondola ride in Venice, and enjoy art and culture in Florence.</p>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4c/Pasta_Dish.jpg" alt="Italian Pasta">
        </section>

        <section class="food">
            <h2>Italian Cuisine</h2>
            <p>Don't miss out on the delightful flavors of Italy! Here are some must-try dishes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Pizza Napoletana</li>
                <li>Risotto alla Milanese</li>
                <li>Tiramisu</li>
                <li>Gelato</li>
                <li>Pasta Carbonara</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Travel Enthusiasts</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
